{"type": "article", "id": 16701, "title": "以色列出现了四朵感应“大花”，给过路行人阴凉", "description": "然而它们出现的有点儿晚了，北半球都进入冬天啦！", "date": "2015-10-28T12:44:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 228, "name": "以色列"}, {"id": 17894, "name": "大花"}, {"id": 17895, "name": "自动感应"}, {"id": 6401, "name": "街区"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 85, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605215100bZmaIwN1zpByDiGE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t在以色列，建筑事务所 <span><a href=\"http://www.hq.co.il/\">HQ Architects</a> </span>设计了四朵<a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/10/27/these-flowers-bloom-when-pedestrians-stand-under-them/\" target=\"_blank\">自动感应的“大花”</a>：它们被放置在人行街道旁，当有行人经过时，花会在自动感应下张开，给行人遮挡阴凉；待行人通过后，花朵又自动闭合了。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052150560esMNG7nJ9BxhRi5.jpg\" title=\"行人路过、花朵张开时\" alt=\"行人路过、花朵张开时\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span>花朵张开时</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215057lhpO251HUnqcyEWT.jpg\" title=\"花朵位于人行步道旁\" alt=\"花朵位于人行步道旁\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">这两个装置<span>位于人行步道旁，显得并不突兀</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215058dg7mikXEYV3284fQ.jpg\" title=\"花朵闭合时\" alt=\"花朵闭合时\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>花朵闭合时</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215058rANGF4nTleV2ktJz.jpg\" title=\"街头\" alt=\"街头\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>街头</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052150583sTw7LC8zgxP9iuh.jpg\" title=\"夜晚时\" alt=\"夜晚时\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>夜晚，大花摇身一变成为路灯</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215059Xi8Myu1AqzthGvUL.jpg\" title=\"花朵下\" alt=\"花朵下\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>花朵下</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215059NtE9QHbioZe2OLhk.jpg\" title=\"设计图\" alt=\"设计图\" data-ratio=\"0.7078125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>设计图</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这四朵大花有 9 米高，花朵张开后的直径也达 9 米。它们位于社区广场的核心位置，坐在这里，可以看到整个广场和对面的市场，当电车到站时，大花也会自动张开，为下车的人遮挡阳光。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t然而它们出现的好像有点儿晚了，北半球已进入冬天，此时人们不需要遮阳，而是巴不得往阳光下跑！\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.contemporist.com/2015/10/27/these-flowers-bloom-when-pedestrians-stand-under-them/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>contemporist</em></a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}